description: Details of revised survey drawings showing works to the at the SE, NE and SW porticos and landings at the NE, NW and SW porticos and a revised schedule of works for these pursuant to part discharge of Condition 10 parts vi and vii, and details of any removed stonework from the porticos, including the steps, must be set aside, and the condition of the removed stonework pursuant to Condition 14 of the listed building consent dated 19 July 2022 (RN: 22/02400/LBC).
